  "prompt": "What companies are similar to IDEO in Paris?",
  "response": "If you are looking for companies similar to IDEO in Paris, you might be interested in design and innovation firms known for their creative problem-solving approaches and human-centered design principles. Some notable companies in Paris include:\n\n1. **Frog Design** - Renowned for its strategic thinking and innovative design solutions, Frog Design focuses on creating meaningful experiences for users.\n\n2. **Fabernovel** - Specializing in digital transformation and innovation consulting, Fabernovel works with companies to embrace new technologies and innovative strategies.\n\n3. **User Studio** - A Paris-based design agency focusing on user experience (UX) and interaction design, User Studio helps businesses create engaging and user-centered products.\n\n4. **Imagination** - This global creative agency offers services in branding, experiential marketing, digital innovation, and design, helping clients create impactful experiences.\n\n5. **Human Interface Group** - Specializes in UX/UI design and digital strategy, working with clients to develop user-centered digital products and services.\n\n6. **Sismo Design** - A design consultancy that blends strategic thinking with product design, focusing on creating innovative solutions tailored to user needs.\n\nThese firms offer services in innovation consulting, product design, user experience (UX) design, and strategic thinking, making them comparable to IDEO in their approach and expertise.",
